         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Office of Lands and Survey ¶ Melbourne, April 21st 1870. ¶ Sir. ¶  ¶ I have the honor to request you will be good enough to instruct Mr Ferguson, ¶ William Ferguson. ¶  ¶ Inspector of State Forests, t...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">70.04.21b</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Clement Hodgkinson</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 70/186, unit 7, p.89, VPRS 7934/P1 outward letter books to other departments and district land offices, VA 538 Department of Crown Lands and Survey, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Office of Lands and Survey</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne, April 21st 1870.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to request you will be good enough to instruct Mr Ferguson,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>William Ferguson.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Inspector of State Forests, to proceed to the site of Messr Anderson Brothers, Sawmills, in the Bullarook Forest,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>At various times all of the six Anderson brothers from Ayreshire, Scotland were involved in saw-milling at Bullarook Forest and flour-milling at Smeaton, Vic. John (1822-1895), James (1824-1901) and William (1826-1886) arrived in South Australia in 1851 and moved to Victoria in 1852. David (1828-1877) and Thomas (1830-1858) who had died before this letter was written arrived in Victoria in 1854 with their brother Robert (1833-1921).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>for the purpose of affording these gentlemen advice and assistance in planting trees in the vicinity or their Mills.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The Honorable the President of the Board of Land and Works having approved of Mr Ferguson being employed on this duty and Messr Anderson paying his expenses, these gentlemen have expressed their willingness so to do.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>You will also be good enough to instruct Mr Ferguson, on his return to Melbourne, to call upon me with the view of inspecting some Murray Pines.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your most obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>C. Hodgkinson</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Asst Commisr<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Assistant Commissioner.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>of Lands &amp; Survey.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Dr Von Mueller</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Government Botanist</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c.<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c.<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c.</p>
         </div>
